          COMPARE   FOUR,TOTPER
          GOTO      CONV9999 IF LESS
          MOVE      SAVDAY,JDAYS
          MOVE      SAVYR,JULYR
          MOVE      SAVCC,JULCC
          MOVE      PERIOD4,DAYS                 * fourth user defined period
          ADD       ONE,DAYS
          CALL      CALC0000
